00:00:30.306 --> 00:00:33.628
<i>Na ta svet</i>

00:00:33.876 --> 00:00:36.636
<i>Svetloba</i>

00:00:36.685 --> 00:00:37.878
<i>S katero sijem</i>

00:00:37.917 --> 00:00:41.261
<i>Dobra je in lepa</i>

00:00:41.524 --> 00:00:44.654
<i>Poglej</i>

00:00:44.723 --> 00:00:46.728
<i>Potovanje se je začelo</i>

00:00:46.773 --> 00:00:50.262
<i>In kako lepa življenja imamo</i>

00:00:55.328 --> 00:00:56.572
Na začetku,

00:00:57.135 --> 00:00:58.999
je bil samo ocean.

00:01:00.097 --> 00:01:03.959
Dokler se ni pojavila "Mati otok".

00:01:04.282 --> 00:01:05.625
Te Fiti.

00:01:06.684 --> 00:01:10.402
Njeno srce je imelo največjo moč.

00:01:10.731 --> 00:01:13.304
Lahko je ustvarilo življenje!

00:01:13.874 --> 00:01:17.578
In Te Fiti ga je podelila s svetom.

00:01:20.516 --> 00:01:24.652
Skozi čas so mnogi iskali
Te Fitino srce.

00:01:25.105 --> 00:01:27.183
Verjeli so, da če si ga lastijo,

00:01:27.283 --> 00:01:30.454
bodo imeli tudi veliko moč ustvarjanja.

00:01:31.096 --> 00:01:32.836
In nekega dne...

00:01:33.759 --> 00:01:36.624
je najupornejši od njih...

00:01:36.775 --> 00:01:40.828
dopotoval preko velikega
oceana, da ga vzame.

00:01:42.589 --> 00:01:46.236
To je bil polbog vetra in morja.

00:01:48.684 --> 00:01:50.198
Bil je vojščak...

00:01:51.602 --> 00:01:52.960
prevarant!

00:01:55.337 --> 00:01:58.144
Metamorf  ki je lahko spreminjal obliko

00:01:58.239 --> 00:02:01.215
s svojim magičnim trnkom.

00:02:03.230 --> 00:02:07.380
Ime mu je bilo Maui!

00:02:17.312 --> 00:02:18.969
Brez njenega srca,

00:02:19.361 --> 00:02:21.246
se je Te Fiti pričela lomiti,

00:02:21.552 --> 00:02:24.702
kar je ustvarilo veliko temo.

00:02:43.194 --> 00:02:44.998
Maui je poskušal pobegniti,

00:02:45.331 --> 00:02:48.547
vendar se je srečal z nekom
drugim, ki je iskal srce.

00:02:51.302 --> 00:02:55.641
Te Ka, demon zemlje in ognja.

00:03:03.691 --> 00:03:06.384
Maui je padel z neba!

00:03:07.745 --> 00:03:09.559
In nihče več ga ni videl.

00:03:10.751 --> 00:03:12.685
Njegov čarobni trnek ...

00:03:12.876 --> 00:03:18.373
in srce Te Fiti,
sta bila izgubljena v morju,

00:03:19.162 --> 00:03:22.745
kjer tudi sedaj, po 1000 letih...

00:03:22.954 --> 00:03:27.710
Te Ka in demoni iz globin, iščejo srce.

00:03:28.242 --> 00:03:32.113
Skrivajo se v temi

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:34.485
in plašijo naše ribe!

00:03:34.707 --> 00:03:38.101
Izčrpavajo življenje z otoka na otok,

00:03:38.210 --> 00:03:44.511
dokler ne bomo vsi požrti
v krvoločnih čeljustih...

00:03:44.578 --> 00:03:47.456
neizogibne smrti!

00:03:52.757 --> 00:03:54.055
Vendar nekega dne...

00:03:54.270 --> 00:03:56.211
bo srce našel

00:03:56.558 --> 00:03:59.603
nekdo, ki bo odšel dlje od grebena,

00:03:59.767 --> 00:04:01.064
našel bo Mauia,

00:04:01.172 --> 00:04:03.291
ga pripeljal preko oceana...

00:04:03.554 --> 00:04:05.682
in vrnil Te Fitino srce...

00:04:05.906 --> 00:04:07.528
da nas vse reši.

00:04:08.619 --> 00:04:10.125
Hvala mati, to bi bilo dovolj.

00:04:10.250 --> 00:04:11.351
Očka...

00:04:11.447 --> 00:04:13.547
Nihče ne potuje dlje od grebena.

00:04:13.549 --> 00:04:14.809
Tukaj smo na varnem!

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:18.342
Ni teme.
Ni pošasti.

00:04:21.649 --> 00:04:23.360
Pošast, pošast!
- Ni pošasti!

00:04:23.430 --> 00:04:24.934
To je tema!

00:04:25.322 --> 00:04:27.957
Ni ničesar izven
našega grebena, razen neviht!

00:04:28.035 --> 00:04:30.018
In burnega morja!
- Slabo mi je!

00:04:30.372 --> 00:04:33.014
Dokler ostanemo na našem otoku,

00:04:33.190 --> 00:04:34.288
bomo dobro!

00:04:34.325 --> 00:04:35.677
Legende so resnične.

00:04:35.726 --> 00:04:37.435
Nekdo bo moral oditi!

00:04:37.585 --> 00:04:38.638
Mati...

00:04:38.719 --> 00:04:40.589
Motunui je raj!

00:04:40.601 --> 00:04:42.431
Zakaj bi nekdo želel oditi kamorkoli?

00:05:19.416 --> 00:05:21.757
Šš!

00:05:56.154 --> 00:06:02.238
<i>Oči imaš tako radovedne</i>

00:06:02.339 --> 00:06:08.725
<i>Srce je nedolžen bojevnik</i>

00:06:09.026 --> 00:06:14.674
<i>Najdražja moja</i>

00:06:14.876 --> 00:06:21.493
<i>Dobila boš nalogo</i>

00:06:21.628 --> 00:06:27.611
<i>Naj te preleti</i>

00:06:27.946 --> 00:06:34.697
<i>Svoboda ki jo občutiš</i>

00:06:34.765 --> 00:06:40.382
<i>In tvoje misli</i>

00:06:40.480 --> 00:06:46.766
<i>Naša mala</i>

00:06:47.801 --> 00:06:53.718
<i>Prišla si</i>

00:06:54.254 --> 00:06:59.971
<i>Mlado dekle</i>

00:07:02.606 --> 00:07:03.636
Moana!

00:07:09.297 --> 00:07:17.297
<i>Oči imaš tako radovedne</i>

00:07:19.019 --> 00:07:21.979
Tu si Moana, kaj delaš,
prestrašila si me!

00:07:22.056 --> 00:07:23.440
Želim se vrniti.

00:07:23.550 --> 00:07:24.553
Vem...

00:07:24.888 --> 00:07:26.445
vendar se ne gre tja.

00:07:27.225 --> 00:07:28.227
Nevarno je.

00:07:30.257 --> 00:07:31.758
Moana, pridi...

00:07:32.672 --> 00:07:33.884
Vrniva se v vas.

00:07:35.977 --> 00:07:38.686
Ti si naslednja v nizu poglavarjev.

00:07:38.779 --> 00:07:41.718
In delala boš čudovite
stvari moja mala Minou.

00:07:41.815 --> 00:07:43.155
O, da, vendar najprej...

00:07:43.355 --> 00:07:46.183
Se moraš naučiti, kje je tvoje mesto.

00:07:58.508 --> 00:07:59.531
Moana...

00:08:00.457 --> 00:08:02.730
Prehod.

00:08:03.061 --> 00:08:04.791
Moana, čas je da spoznaš.

00:08:05.143 --> 00:08:08.863
Vas Motunui je vse kar potrebuješ.

00:08:09.268 --> 00:08:10.972
Glasbeniki vadijo

00:08:11.209 --> 00:08:13.178
Igrajo po starem ritmu.

00:08:13.291 --> 00:08:16.571
Kdo potrebuje novo pesem?
Stara je vse kar potrebuješ.

00:08:16.619 --> 00:08:18.632
Ta tradicija je naša misija.

00:08:18.688 --> 00:08:21.069
Moana, toliko je za narediti.

00:08:21.443 --> 00:08:25.191
Ne spotikaj se na taro koren.
In to je vse.

00:08:25.442 --> 00:08:27.148
Delimo vse kar napravimo.

00:08:27.616 --> 00:08:29.441
Šalimo se in delamo koše.

00:08:29.646 --> 00:08:31.999
Ribiči se vračajo z ribolova.

00:08:32.037 --> 00:08:35.277
Hočem videti.
- Ne odhajaj.

00:08:35.701 --> 00:08:37.678
Moana ostani na tleh.

00:08:37.789 --> 00:08:41.674
Ljudem bo potreben
poglavar in to si ti...

00:08:41.775 --> 00:08:43.371
Prišel bo dan

00:08:43.900 --> 00:08:45.694
ko se boš obrnila.

00:08:45.902 --> 00:08:49.928
In spoznala, da je sreča tu kjer si.

00:08:50.005 --> 00:08:51.630
Poglej,  kokosov oreh!

00:08:52.140 --> 00:08:54.108
Poglej steblo...

00:08:54.128 --> 00:08:55.593
Uporabimo vse.

00:08:55.607 --> 00:08:57.814
Kar potrebujemo.

00:08:58.075 --> 00:09:00.240
Delamo mreže iz vlaken.

00:09:00.269 --> 00:09:02.135
Voda je sladka.

00:09:02.307 --> 00:09:04.198
Z listjem zakurimo ogenj.

00:09:04.245 --> 00:09:06.009
Kuhamo meso.

00:09:06.293 --> 00:09:07.997
Poglej kokos!

00:09:08.202 --> 00:09:10.426
Vse iz njega!

00:09:10.439 --> 00:09:12.888
Otok nam daje vse.

00:09:12.904 --> 00:09:16.019
In nihče ne odhaja.
- Tako je, ostajamo.

00:09:16.448 --> 00:09:18.468
Na varnem smo in dobro nam je.

00:09:18.593 --> 00:09:20.425
In ko gledamo v prihodnost...

00:09:20.473 --> 00:09:22.588
Tu si ti.

00:09:22.633 --> 00:09:24.297
Dobro boš.

00:09:24.609 --> 00:09:26.648
Naučila se boš, kot jaz.

00:09:26.818 --> 00:09:31.933
Moraš najti srečo tu kjer si!

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:39.009
Rada plešem pri vodi.

00:09:39.173 --> 00:09:41.078
S plimo in valovi.

00:09:41.221 --> 00:09:43.006
Voda je poredna!

00:09:43.358 --> 00:09:45.041
Všeč mi, ko pljuska.

00:09:45.394 --> 00:09:47.509
Vas misli, da sem prismuknjena.

00:09:47.562 --> 00:09:49.321
Ali da grem daleč

00:09:49.669 --> 00:09:54.519
Vendar ko dojameš kaj ljubiš, ostaneš tu.

00:09:56.167 --> 00:09:57.975
Si hčerka svojega očeta.

00:09:58.525 --> 00:10:00.164
Trmoglavost in ponos.

00:10:00.288 --> 00:10:02.430
Pazi kaj govori, vendar pazi.

00:10:02.641 --> 00:10:04.512
Lahko slišiš notranji glas...

00:10:09.281 --> 00:10:10.284
Oče!

00:10:10.437 --> 00:10:11.971
Samo gledala sem čolne.

00:10:12.085 --> 00:10:13.721
Nisem se hotela povzpeti.

00:10:17.697 --> 00:10:18.700
Pridi.

00:10:18.733 --> 00:10:20.436
Moram ti nekaj pokazati.

00:10:23.054 --> 00:10:26.472
Hotel sem te pripeljati sem
takoj ko si se rodila.

00:10:27.407 --> 00:10:29.081
To je sveto mesto,

00:10:29.681 --> 00:10:31.009
mesto poglavarja.

00:10:31.650 --> 00:10:33.000
Prišel bo čas

00:10:33.461 --> 00:10:35.984
ko boš stala tukaj in postavila...

00:10:36.326 --> 00:10:38.212
kamen na to planino.

00:10:38.645 --> 00:10:39.648
Kot jaz.

00:10:39.909 --> 00:10:41.131
Kot moj oče.

00:10:41.478 --> 00:10:44.845
In njegovega očeta oče in vseh poglavarjev,
ki so obstajali.

00:10:46.016 --> 00:10:53.217
In tega dne, ko boš dodajala
svoj kamen, boš dvignila cel otok.

00:10:54.110 --> 00:10:56.212
Ti si prihodnost našega ljudstva, Moana.

00:10:56.823 --> 00:10:58.517
Ljudstvo ni tam,

00:10:59.610 --> 00:11:01.477
temveč tukaj.

00:11:02.663 --> 00:11:05.173
Čas je, da postaneš to kar moraš.

00:11:07.503 --> 00:11:09.509
Delamo mreže iz vlaken.
- Pletemo mreže iz vlaken

00:11:09.565 --> 00:11:11.450
Voda je sladka.
- Pravi okus drevesa.

00:11:11.474 --> 00:11:13.680
Uporabljamo listje da delamo ogenj.
- Pojemo v zborih.

00:11:13.737 --> 00:11:15.514
Kuhamo meso.
- Ker imamo usta za hraniti.

00:11:15.635 --> 00:11:17.727
Vas verjame v nas.
- Tako je!

00:11:17.811 --> 00:11:19.734
Vas verjame!

00:11:19.787 --> 00:11:22.022
Otok nam daje kar potrebujemo.

00:11:22.047 --> 00:11:25.457
in nihče ne odhaja!
Pa bom tudi jaz ostala.

00:11:25.866 --> 00:11:27.674
Moj dom in ljudje poleg mene.

00:11:27.890 --> 00:11:29.742
In ko mislim na prihodnost.

00:11:29.757 --> 00:11:31.985
Tu smo vsi.

00:11:32.013 --> 00:11:33.550
Vodil jih bom.

00:11:33.927 --> 00:11:35.899
Ljudje me bodo vodili.

00:11:36.149 --> 00:11:38.048
Gradili bomo prihodnost skupaj.

00:11:38.072 --> 00:11:40.029
Ker smo tu.

00:11:40.050 --> 00:11:41.978
Ker vsaka pot te vodi...

00:11:42.012 --> 00:11:44.219
tja kjer si.

00:11:44.257 --> 00:11:47.807
Našla boš srečo...
- Tu kjer si.

00:11:47.946 --> 00:11:51.403
Tu kjer si....

00:11:55.139 --> 00:11:58.479
Vsakič ko pada dež, streha pušča
ne glede na to, s koliko listja pokrijem.

00:11:58.519 --> 00:11:59.521
Popravljeno!

00:11:59.547 --> 00:12:00.917
Poveži listje!

00:12:03.227 --> 00:12:04.810
Veter je premaknil steber.

00:12:06.227 --> 00:12:07.403
To je dobra svinjina!

00:12:10.224 --> 00:12:11.520
Oh, mislim...

00:12:11.718 --> 00:12:12.721
Ne, nisem...

00:12:12.777 --> 00:12:15.306
Kaj, kličejo me, moram ...

00:12:15.864 --> 00:12:16.867
Čao!

00:12:19.478 --> 00:12:20.806
Dobro ti gre.

00:12:20.859 --> 00:12:22.113
Ali je gotovo?

00:12:24.378 --> 00:12:25.548
Blizu.

00:12:40.302 --> 00:12:42.200
Sprašujem v zvezi tega piščanca.

00:12:42.326 --> 00:12:43.517
Je kamen!

00:12:43.545 --> 00:12:48.642
Mislim da mu manjka
osnovne inteligence za vse.

00:12:48.979 --> 00:12:50.324
Ali ga naj...

00:12:50.643 --> 00:12:51.646
Skuhamo?

00:12:52.903 --> 00:12:55.656
Včasih se naša moč
skriva za površnostjo.

00:12:57.749 --> 00:12:58.751
Zelo zadaj...

00:12:58.805 --> 00:13:00.193
marsikdaj.

00:13:00.400 --> 00:13:03.408
Vendar sem prepričana da
Hei-hei ni toliko površen!

00:13:10.667 --> 00:13:11.912
Žetev je.

00:13:12.201 --> 00:13:15.003
Zjutraj sem nabirala kokose in...

00:13:22.081 --> 00:13:23.083
In..

00:13:23.372 --> 00:13:25.141
Morali bi posekati obolela stebla.

00:13:25.585 --> 00:13:29.287
In posadimo nova,
tam!

00:13:31.967 --> 00:13:32.969
Hvala ti, Moana.

00:13:33.260 --> 00:13:34.757
Dobro ji gre!

00:13:39.426 --> 00:13:40.627
To ti pristaja.

00:13:40.895 --> 00:13:41.898
Poglavar!

00:13:42.993 --> 00:13:44.397
Moraš nekaj videti.

00:13:45.404 --> 00:13:46.955
Naše pasti v vzhodni laguni.

00:13:47.255 --> 00:13:48.946
Prinašajo vse manjše ribe.

00:13:49.621 --> 00:13:52.085
Potem bomo premaknili pasti.

00:13:52.538 --> 00:13:54.164
Smo, ni ribe.

00:13:55.677 --> 00:13:57.855
Potem bomo lovili na
oddaljeni strani otoka.

00:13:57.874 --> 00:13:58.877
Poskušali smo.

00:13:59.221 --> 00:14:00.431
Vetrovni strani?

00:14:00.454 --> 00:14:01.631
Potem na nevetrovni.

00:14:01.718 --> 00:14:02.946
Plitvine, kanal.

00:14:03.198 --> 00:14:04.827
Preizkusili smo celo laguno!

00:14:05.368 --> 00:14:07.107
Rib ni.

00:14:07.869 --> 00:14:09.634
Ste poizkušali z drugačno vabo?

00:14:09.760 --> 00:14:11.268
Mislim da ni problem v vabi.

00:14:18.100 --> 00:14:19.633
Pogovoril se bom s svetom.

00:14:19.651 --> 00:14:21.015
Prepričan sem...
- Kaj če...

00:14:21.218 --> 00:14:22.630
lovimo izven grebena!

00:14:24.540 --> 00:14:26.415
Nihče ne bo šel dlje od grebena.

00:14:26.540 --> 00:14:29.221
Vem, vendar če ni rib v laguni...

00:14:29.322 --> 00:14:30.981
Moana!
- A tu je cel ocean...

00:14:31.006 --> 00:14:32.606
Imamo eno pravilo!

00:14:32.621 --> 00:14:34.306
Staro pravilo, ko so bile ribe!

00:14:34.306 --> 00:14:36.028
Pravilo zaradi katerega smo varni!

00:14:36.051 --> 00:14:38.068
Ampak oče...
- Namesto da ogrožamo naš narod

00:14:38.078 --> 00:14:39.934
da tečeš do vode!

00:14:47.253 --> 00:14:49.965
Vsakič ko pomislim
da si šla preko tega.

00:14:52.377 --> 00:14:54.377
Nihče ne gre ven iz grebena!

00:15:01.290 --> 00:15:06.270
Ni ravno da si to rekla
očetu stoječ na čolnu.

00:15:07.104 --> 00:15:09.482
Nisem rekla da gremo ven iz grebena

00:15:09.491 --> 00:15:11.603
ker želim biti na oceanu.

00:15:11.631 --> 00:15:13.183
Ali želiš.

00:15:15.156 --> 00:15:17.513
Znaša se nad teboj, ker...
- Ker me ne razume.

00:15:17.604 --> 00:15:20.010
Ker je bil kot ti.

00:15:21.268 --> 00:15:22.666
Ocean ga je privlačil.

00:15:23.042 --> 00:15:24.388
Obala ga je privlačila.

00:15:25.313 --> 00:15:26.899
Vzel je kanu, Moana.

00:15:27.429 --> 00:15:29.088
Šel preko grebena.

00:15:29.744 --> 00:15:32.197
In prišel na morje ki ne oprošča.

00:15:32.622 --> 00:15:34.733
Valovi kot planine.

00:15:35.683 --> 00:15:38.176
Najboljšega prijatelja je
prosil da ostane na ladji.

00:15:39.120 --> 00:15:40.576
Tvoj oče ga ni mogel rešiti.

00:15:43.747 --> 00:15:45.860
Upa, da bo rešil vsaj tebe.

00:15:48.353 --> 00:15:51.273
Včasih, ko si želimo biti kdo drug,

00:15:51.976 --> 00:15:53.640
da bi nekaj napravili...

00:15:55.627 --> 00:15:57.522
nam ni usojeno.

00:16:12.022 --> 00:16:16.247
Stojim in gledam v vodo.

00:16:16.331 --> 00:16:22.568
Do koder se spomnim in ne vem zakaj

00:16:23.097 --> 00:16:28.173
Želim biti popolna hčerka

00:16:28.333 --> 00:16:34.084
Vendar se vračam k vodi,
poskušajoč, da tega ne bi počela

00:16:35.795 --> 00:16:38.765
Kamorkoli grem
vsaka pot, ki jo prehodim

00:16:38.880 --> 00:16:41.638
Vse me vodi do

00:16:41.793 --> 00:16:44.555
točke, kamor ne morem

00:16:44.625 --> 00:16:47.148
Kjer želim biti

00:16:47.241 --> 00:16:49.574
Da vidim mesto kjer se
spajata nebo in zemlja?

